PAMAGARAL - ING UMPISA


Ing Pamagaral Magumpisa pa ketang balang Lelangan atyu pa king Atyan ning Inda.

Oyni ing kapanwalan at tuturu ring batikan karing pamanigaral karing anak ngene. Pnagabayit na ning pungul potang mapatlud ne pangatayid pusad king Inda, magi neng bingut a malaya. Keni ne ing umpisa ning keyang Kalayan anting metung a tau, ngara ring doktor at batikan karing anak a mangalati.

Ing kalayan ning pamisip yang maragul a saup king pamagaral at pangabyasa ning tau.

Metung karing tawling bayaning ning Educacion/Pamanguan Kabyasnan Pilipinas yapin i Raul Roco. Reng tutuki meyakwa la karing mapilan nang pamangamanu:


 " ... busten ye ikuwentu ku ining makuyad a istorya bangkanita atandanan yu ing sukat nang dalan a panamdam ning Pi Sigma Fraternity. Ngana kekatang Albert Camus, anyang susulat ya ketang mangalungkut rang aldo ring Pransis anyang eganagana maralumdum, ngana, "King kalibudtan ning Karimlan, ikit ku king kakung sarili ing e masakup a Kapalyan."  Ikatamu anti mong buklud, ikatamu anti mong tau, ikatmu anti mong talapagaral, ikatmu anti mong Filipino, sukat tang akit king sarili tamu ngening aldo ayni, agyang atin nang panamdam a alang asahan, itang e masakup a kapalyan anti mong metung a mabayanyan at mapan-yuyung Filipinu." (Palakpakan)

"Ing kuwentu nang Paul Cezanne, ing talagulist, ating yang ditak a pangayalwa pero pareu ya buring sabyan. Paul Cezanne, ing amu ring kulol, atyu king silid metung a masanting abak at reng anggang kurtina makasara la.  Ating yang dinatang a bisita a sinabi kayang, "Tara lumwal kata at yamyaman ta ing sala." Oneng anang Paul Cezanne, "Ali, bisa kung lukluk keni."  Ngana ning kaluguran na, "Malyari kong buklat ding kurtina muman, at paburen lungub ing sala ning aldo?"  Anang Cezanne, "Pakisabing mayap ali mu paburen lulub ing sala ning aldo uling abalanan na ing kulol a akakit ku kanaku."  Eku balu nung pigunamgunaman ya mu o tutu yang kuwentu, pero kasanting nung atulid naka tamu paglalawe anting mong balayan bangkanita akit taya ing sala king sarili tamu. Nung ing gubiernu ena aluwal ita ikatamu na,  ring memalen, ing miluwal."

"Bilang pagtatapos, sapagkat magsasalita pa ang ating brod, let me tell you a little story that may make you remember the sense that the Pi Sigma Fraternity must have. We are told by Albert Camus, when he was writing during the sad days of the French and things looked bleak, he said, "In the midst of winter, I found within myself an invincible summer." We as a fraternity, we as a people, we as students, we as Filipinos, must find within ourselves today, even if there is a sense of hopelessness, the invincible summer of being a patriotic and service-oriented Filipino." (Applause).

"The story of Paul Cezanne, the artist, is a little different but it gives the same meaning. Paul Cezanne, the master of color, was in his room one fine morning and all the curtains were closed. And his friend visited him and said, "Let us go out and enjoy the sunlight." But Paul Cezanne said, "No, I want to sit here." And the friend said, "Can I at least open the curtains and let the sunlight in?" And Paul Cezanne said, "Please do not let the sunlight in because it will disturb the colors I see within me." I do not know if that is apocryphal or a true story, but it is great to make us focus that we as a people must find the light within us. If the government cannot bring that out, then the people must bring it out."
                      

Extemporaneous Speech of Raul S. Roco
Homecoming of UP Pi Sigma Association
Bahay ng Alumni, UP Diliman, Quezon City
August 17, 2002

Metung yang masanting a patune ning kalayan ning pamisip ining kuwentu kang Cezanne a simbitla nang Meanguabie Raul Roco, metung karing mayap a talapamunu at abogadu.  Pepakit na naman ing keyang lugud at nasang sumuyu pang lalu king keyang Bansa at kaburyan miyampang king keyang bie keng kingwa nang kataya nang Albert Camus.  Kalakolako napa  ning Senador ngening Ka-5 nang Aldo ning Agosto, 2005, petsa keni California, USA, bang mamayapa kayabe ning Miglalang kaya.
